bug.description: Some of <denchmark-link:http://open3d.org/docs/tutorial/Basic/rgbd_odometry.html>Open3D's python tutorial</denchmark-link> utilizes <denchmark-link:http://redwood-data.org/indoor/dataset.html>Redwood dataset</denchmark-link> . Redwood dataset is a synthetic dataset made with PrimeSenseDefault parameter, but TestData/camera.json file used by the tutorials is not the parameter of PrimeSenseDefault.
